parameters:
Dining Hall Chef: Are you interested in helping with the
cooking?

Dining Hall Chef: Oh dear, I have to figure something out
myself.

Dining Hall Chef: Thank goodness! Come with me to the
kitchen!

Dining Hall Chef: I'm really grateful, if you're willing,
please take it!
Dining Hall Chef: Ahaha... Are you okay?

Cafeteria Staff: Welcome! We use fresh vegetables and
cheese.

Busy Woman: I need to eat quickly and get back to work!
Taking care of the cows, preparing the cheese... I have so
much to do!

Farmer Man: It's better not to approach the grassland area.
It's a really dangerous place with many bandits.

Male Worker: The nobles here are too rough with their
treatment of people... Oops... I shouldn't be talking about
this to a traveler.

Exhausted man: I want to change the current situation where
my son has joined a band of thieves... even though the only
thing that changes is our lifespan... ugh.
